      "message": "Don\u0027t use MACRO_CAPITALS for types, even if they are enum, just use CamelCase as usual, and try to make the name more explicit, as in \"CommunicationState\"\n\nIt\u0027s also generally a good idea to document the values of an enum when there are more than 2 or 3 of them. Especially since this is a state-machine, document the possible transitions between these values, this will help better understand the rest of the code.",
